AWS Deployment (EC2 + Docker Compose) — ap-south-1 (Mumbai)

Deployed on AWS EC2 t3.small instance running Ubuntu 24.04. Frontend (Next.js) and Backend (FastAPI) containerized using 
Docker Compose. Nginx configured as reverse proxy on port 80. Region selected: ap-south-1 (Mumbai) for India-first latency
optimization.


Azure Deployment (Container Apps) — Central India

Deployed on Azure Container Apps using a serverless container architecture. Docker images pushed to Azure Container Registry 
(ACR). Frontend and Backend running as separate Container Apps with auto-scaling (min 1, max 3 replicas). 
Region selected: Central India for consistency with AWS India region strategy.


